<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - WanderInn</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/backend/public/privacyPolicy.css">
</head>

<body>
    <section class="privacyPolicyContainer">
        <div class="loginInnerBox">
            <h1>Privacy Policy for WanderInn</h1>
            <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: 02/06/2025</p>

            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to WanderInn, a hotel booking demo app. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
                disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our application. By accessing or using WanderInn,
                you consent to the practices outlined in this policy.</p>

            <h2>2. Information Collection and Use</h2>
            <p>We collect various types of information to provide and improve our services, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal Information: Name, email, phone number, payment details.</li>
                <li>Login Credentials: To authenticate user access.</li>
                <li>Booking Details: Hotels, dates, and other preferences.</li>
                <li>Device Information: IP address, browser type, and app usage data.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Parental Consent</h2>
            <p>WanderInn is not intended for children under 13. If we discover that a child has provided personal
                information without parental consent, we will take steps to delete such information.</p>

            <h2>4. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We do not sell or trade your personal information. However, we may share data with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Service providers assisting with payments and bookings.</li>
                <li>Law enforcement agencies when required by law.</li>
                <li>Affiliates or partners to improve services.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission
                over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

            <h2>6. Access to and Deletion of Information</h2>
            <p>You can request to access, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us.</p>

            <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>WanderInn may contain links to third-party services, such as hotel providers. We are not responsible for
                their privacy practices.</p>

            <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised
                "Last Updated" date.</p>

            <h2>9. Your Acceptance of These Terms</h2>
            <p>By using WanderInn, you accept this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please discontinue using our
                services.</p>

            <h2>10. Contacting Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out:</p>
            <p>
                WanderInn Support<br />
                <%= process.env.CONTACT_SUPPORT_MAIL %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@9"></script>
</body>

</html>